When building from sources

Pre-requisites
--------------

- Ocaml compiler (>=4.06) with the following packages installed (preferably using OPAM 2) :
  . ocamlfind
  . ocamlbuild
  . ocamlgraph
  . menhir
  . lascar
  
- a working Qt5 installation

Building
--------

Decompress the archive, cd to the source directory and type :

1. ./configure [options]
2. ./make
3. ./make install
